{"word":"διερέσσω","slug":"διερέσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διερέσσω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ερέσω</el>) (aor1 <el>-ήρεσα</el>) (<a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> <el>-ήρεσσα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to row about</i>, <el>χερσὶ δ.</el> to swim, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <el>δ. τὰς χέρας</el> <i>to swing</i> them <i>about</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}